cell.grid

Class CellGridGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • cell.grid.CellGridGenerator

  • public class CellGridGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    A static tool for creating CellGrid structures of predefined size.
    The different dimensions are not explicitly specified in the documentation!
